        <hl1>Pausing to Remember a Cardinal</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Cardinal O'Connor, 80, Dies; Forceful Voice for Vatican'' (front page, May 4):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Cardinal O'Connor, 80, Dies; Forceful Voice for Vatican'' (front page, May 4):</p>
        <p>As a 24-year-old Roman Catholic, I very much respected and admired Cardinal John O'Connor. He was a man of courage, conviction and compassion. May he rest in peace.</p>
        <p>MATT C. ABBOTT  Chicago, May 4, 2000</p>
      </block>
